        R10 is H, alkyl, or aryl;
        each R11 is independently H or alkyl;
        r is 0, 1, 2, or 3; and
        s is 1, 2, 3, or 4;

provided that:

        at least two of Rc, Rd, and Re are other than H; and
        when R1, R6, R7, and R8 are each H, then Rd and Re taken together form a bicycloalkyl or tricycloalkyl ring;
        or a pharmaceutically acceptable salt thereof.

